{
    "id": "objectInteractions",
    "name": "Object Interactions",
    "isScript": false,
    "description": "A configurable interaction system for objects that enables various player actions including pickup, drop, push, pull, and inventory placement. Provides physics-based object manipulation with customizable interaction settings.",
    "documentation": "## Object Interactions\nEnable player interactions with scene objects.\n\n### Available Interactions\n- **Pick Up** - Player can pick up the object\n- **Drop** - Player can drop a held object\n- **Push** - Player can push the object (auto on contact, or with E if pickup is disabled)\n- **Pull** - Player can pull the object (auto on contact when facing away, or with P)\n- **Place In Inventory** - Object is added to inventory and removed from scene\n\n### Controls\n- Press **E** to activate an interaction (pick up / push)\n- Press **F** to deactivate (drop)\n- Press **P** to pull a nearby object toward you\n\n### Tips\n- Enable physics on the object for push/pull to work\n- Multiple interactions can be enabled on the same object",
    "author": "stemstudio",
    "tags": ["object interaction"],
    "main": "ObjectInteractionsBehavior.ts",
    "version": "1.1.0",
    "dependencies": {},
    "throttleConfig": {
        "throttlePriority": "HIGH",
        "enableFrustumCulling": true,
        "enableDistanceThrottling": false,
        "requiresConsistentUpdates": true
    },
    "attributes": {
        "customName": {
            "name": "Custom Name",
            "type": "string"
        },
        "pickUp": {
            "name": "Pick Up",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When enabled, the player can pick up this object by pressing the interact key.",
            "default": true
        },
        "drop": {
            "name": "Drop",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When enabled, the player can drop this object after picking it up.",
            "default": true
        },
        "push": {
            "name": "Push",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When enabled, the player can push this object using physics. Requires physics to be enabled on the object.",
            "default": true
        },
        "pull": {
            "name": "Pull",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When enabled, the player can pull this object toward them. Requires physics to be enabled on the object.",
            "default": true
        },
        "placeInInventory": {
            "name": "Place In Inventory",
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "When enabled, the object is placed into the player's inventory on interaction instead of being held.",
            "default": false
        },
        "separator1": {
            "type": "separator"
        },
        "interactionDistance": {
            "name": "Interaction Distance",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0.5,
            "max": 20,
            "default": 3.5
        },
        "interactionCooldownMs": {
            "name": "Interaction Cooldown (ms)",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 2000,
            "default": 150
        },
        "interactionMass": {
            "name": "Interaction Mass",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0.1,
            "max": 1000,
            "default": 1
        },
        "separator2": {
            "type": "separator"
        },
        "holdDistance": {
            "name": "Hold Distance",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0.2,
            "max": 8,
            "default": 1.75
        },
        "holdHeight": {
            "name": "Hold Height",
            "type": "number",
            "min": -2,
            "max": 6,
            "default": 1.1
        },
        "holdSideOffset": {
            "name": "Hold Side Offset",
            "type": "number",
            "min": -5,
            "max": 5,
            "default": 0
        },
        "rotateWithPlayer": {
            "name": "Rotate With Player",
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": true
        },
        "separator3": {
            "type": "separator"
        },
        "pushImpulse": {
